&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real-world preparation:&lt;/strong&gt; Learn about Motivational Interviewing, care coordination, and how to help patients navigate social needs such as food, housing, and transportation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Culture of support:&lt;/strong&gt; Dedicated trainers, clinical mentors, and peer cohorts guide you every step of the way.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At the end of your apprenticeship, you’ll complete a sign-off process to begin full-time patient care with the knowledge, tools, and community to succeed.&lt;/p&gt;
